# BoycottScanner

### Local Dev
#### Start Metro
Metro is the javascript bundler that ships with React Native

`npx react-native start`

#### Run instructions for iOS (must be on mac):
`npx react-native run-ios`
    - or -
Open BoycottScanner/ios/BoycottScanner.xcworkspace in Xcode or run "xed -b ios"
Hit the Run button
    - or -
`./node_modules/react-native/scripts/launchPackager.command ; exit;`

#### Run instructions for Android:
Have an Android emulator running (quickest way to get started), or a device connected.
`npx react-native run-android`
